## Distribution Comparison Table

| Method | Best For... | Setup Difficulty | Teacher Effort |
| --- | --- | --- | --- |
| **LTI** | Institutional Adoption | High | Low (Built into Canvas) |
| **Heroku** | Centralized Hosting | Medium | Low (Just a URL) |
| **Git** | Developer Backup | Low | High (They must host it) |
| **Extension** | Individual Power-Users | Medium | Medium (Must install) |

